 call a few hours ago. \nOn way to see my father probably for the last time, he had a \u201clarge\u201d stroke in the brain stem, per doctors.\n\nHe is a warrior, a wonderful father and person, and as MAGA as there is. \n\nAsking for prayers.\n\nEdit: I want to thank every one of you for taking the time to comment and pray. It means an enormous amount to me, I can\u2019t even put it to words. It fills me with hope, knowing there are people like you all out there and it\u2019s brought some light to this very dark time. Thank you all. \n\n\n", "author": "Boobzrule", "created": 1772997156627, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Klaus73", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Asking for prayers for my dad ", "last_comment_created": 1773059648666, "content": "<p>Hey pedes,</p>\n<p>Got the worst phone call a few hours ago.\nOn way to see my father probably for the last time, he had a \u201clarge\u201d stroke in the brain stem, per doctors.</p>\n<p>He is a warrior, a wonderful father and person, and as MAGA as there is.</p>\n<p>Asking for prayers.</p>\n<p>Edit: I want to thank every one of you for taking the time to comment and pray. It means an enormous amount to me, I can\u2019t even put it to words. It fills me with hope, knowing there are people like you all out there and it\u2019s brought some light to this very dark time. Thank you all.</p>\n", "score_down": 3, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 78, "score_up": 1031, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "t